  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Environmental Education: Eco-kids for Future</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims at connecting 200 kids and 20 youths to nature. It focuses on enhancing environmental awareness among children and develops environmental ethics and makes them environmentally conscious citizens. These kids/youths will also be involved in the planting of 2000 (Prunus Africana) and bio-monitoring aimed to conserve their long-degraded community forest and water catchment serving 10,000 persons.  Eco clubs will be created and the holding of outdoor and mega competitions.</narrative>
  </description>
